snippet.title: The Only One Girl (Opening - 1stQ ver.)
snippet.description:
The opening for our upcoming free visual novel "The Only One Girl". This is for the short version release "{ First Quarter }". All dialogue is fully voiced! (Expand description for links about the project)

[ Keep Up To Date With The Project ]
Our GameJolt page;
http://gamejolt.com/games/the-only-one-girl/147270
Lemmasoft thread;
https://lemmasoft.renai.us/forums/viewtopic.php?f=43&t=40800

CREDITS~
Sprites by Elzee
Other artworks by fuicchi, TheFreePotato, Dighm Liting, holey_cheese
Backgrounds: Uncle Mugen, PeaSoft, morguefile
Video by Kokoro Hane

Song used - "Door" by SENTiVE
http://sentive.net/
